    "content": "This application shows an example of using the FAT File System to access and modify the contents of a SD card using the SDMMC driver . ",
    "url": "http://localhost:4000/core_apps_sam_e70_s70_v70_v71/apps/fs/sdmmc_fat/readme.html#fat-filesystem-using-sdmmc-media",
